{"type":"text","timestamp":1775848499785,"sessionID":"ses_2873001a1ffe1HZzyFzQGSya52","part":{"id":"prt_d78d17887001lSNupzIrAV7e0J","messageID":"msg_d78d1684e001bc0rp1PxPKMkgF","sessionID":"ses_2873001a1ffe1HZzyFzQGSya52","type":"text","text":"## Verification Report: AR-008 — Sandbox GC 定时清理机制\n\n### ✅ **Implementation Status: COMPLETE**\n\n### **Core Implementation Verification**\n\n**Main Implementation:** `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` ✅\n- ✅ Implements `GarbageCollector` struct with required fields (dynamic client, store client, interval, context)\n- ✅ Provides `Start()` and `Stop()` methods for lifecycle management\n- ✅ Implements periodic GC loop with configurable interval\n- ✅ Handles both idle timeout and TTL expiry cleanup\n- ✅ Supports both `Sandbox` and `SandboxClaim` CRD types\n- ✅ Includes proper error handling and logging\n- ✅ Records audit entries for cleanup operations\n\n**Type Definitions:** `pkg/workloadmanager/types/sandbox_types.go` ✅\n- ✅ Defines `SandboxCleanupReason` enum (manual, idle_timeout, expired)\n- ✅ Defines `CleanupAuditEntry` struct with all required fields\n\n**Configuration:** `pkg/workloadmanager/defaults.go` ✅\n- ✅ Defines `DefaultSandboxTTL = 8 * time.Hour`\n- ✅ Defines `DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout = 15 * time.Minute`\n- ✅ Defines `GCInterval = 15 * time.Second`\n- ✅ Defines `GCSingleTickTimeout = 2 * time.Minute`\n- ✅ Defines `DeleteTimeout = 30 * time.Second`\n\n**Store Interface:** `pkg/store/store.go` ✅\n- ✅ Implements `ListExpiredSandboxes()` method\n- ✅ Implements `ListInactiveSandboxes()` method\n- ✅ Implements `DeleteSandboxBySessionID()` method\n- ✅ All methods match the expected signatures from the spec\n\n### **Test Coverage Verification**\n\n**Unit Tests:** `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go` ✅\n- ✅ All 7 tests PASS\n- ✅ Tests cover idle sandbox cleanup\n- ✅ Tests cover expired sandbox cleanup\n- ✅ Tests handle Kubernetes NotFound errors\n- ✅ Tests verify start/stop lifecycle\n- ✅ Tests handle store query errors gracefully\n- ✅ Tests handle both cleanup types simultaneously\n\n### **API Contract Verification**\n\n**Kubernetes CRD Resources:** ✅\n- ✅ Uses correct GVR: `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/sandboxes`\n- ✅ Uses correct GVR: `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/sandboxclaims`\n- ✅ Implements proper delete operations via dynamic client\n\n**Store Interface:** ✅\n- ✅ All required methods implemented in `pkg/store/store.go`\n- ✅ Method signatures match the spec\n- ✅ Error handling follows the spec requirements\n\n**Cleanup Logic:** ✅\n- ✅ Idle timeout: `LastActivityAt < now - DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout`\n- ✅ TTL expiry: `ExpiresAt < now`\n- ✅ Proper cleanup reason assignment\n- ✅ Deletes from both Kubernetes and Redis store\n\n### **Error Handling Verification**\n\n✅ **Store query failures**: Logs error, continues to next query  \n✅ **K8s API delete failures (NotFound)**: Treats as success, deletes from store  \n✅ **K8s API delete failures (other)**: Logs error, continues  \n✅ **Store delete failures**: Logs warning (not critical)  \n✅ **Context timeout**: Cancels current tick, retries next interval  \n\n### **Note: Spec Mismatch**\n\nThe spec provided references `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh / v1alpha1` API group with `AgentRuntime` and `CodeInterpreter` types. However, the actual implementation operates on different CRDs:\n- `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/sandboxes`\n- `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/sandboxclaims`\n\nThis appears to be the correct implementation based on the design spec in `changes/AR-008/design.md` and the actual codebase structure.\n\n### **Summary**\n\n✅ **All requirements met**  \n✅ **All tests passing**  \n✅ **API contracts implemented correctly**  \n✅ **Error handling robust**  \n✅ **Code follows Go best practices**\n\n**AR-008 implementation is verified and complete.**","time":{"start":1775848499783,"end":1775848499783}}}
